End a tiring day, drifting off to sleep with the sound of rain. The sound washes away heavy thoughts, freeing them from thought. Time, don't forget, you are precious!

On an ordinary night, the sound of rain gurgles, its dripping echoing in its own voice. The night holds a romantic melody, a harmony of nature, its patter cleansing the dust from the soul.

Time must eventually pass, the night twinkles with shooting stars. The rain unfolds a boundless journey, imagining drifting on a planet of rain.
